::Killfest::

Killfest nods, watching them clear the edge. "This time, yes."

He powers up his jetpack again, setting it on full power. It would 
give them quite a bit of distance, but if they did clear the hole, it 
would be a bumpy landing, as the jetpack was running out of fuel.
